      "content": "but i really don't want to go to the hospital if i don't have to. it's so expensive and the waiting rooms are awful. i know my body and i know how my anxiety feels. it's more of a dull weight than sharp pain. can you just help me figure out if it's definitely just stress? maybe i can just take a sedative and sleep it off?",
