      "content": "i understand but i'm just so stressed about the cost. my husband has had this happen before and the doctor just told him it was psychosomatic and he felt fine after just resting. if the weight is just dull/dullish and not sharp, is it even possible it's my heart? cant i just monitor it for a few hours and if it doesn't get sharper i'll be okay?",
